{"tid":1683822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月11號 全港一連三日大罷工 請即行動 全力文宣 堅持落去","createTime":"2019-10-30T21:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T01:33:12.000Z","uid":134033,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"82c062487d25b9b7a4dfbcb242ebcdf008c7f4c3","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:08:47.000Z","msg":"相信各位手足心水都清 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">即使去到如此黑暗既時代<br />\n<br />\n成個香港都未準備好全民勇武</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真正夠膽出去以命攬炒 我估全港唔到二十個人<br />\n<br />\n既然當刻呢個方法唔可行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">請停止一切互屌 分化 灰心行為<br />\n<br />\n用實質行動去証明  追求自由既決心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才 為左尊重番現有既行動 手足既付出<br />\n<br />\n參考番最新日程表  決定11號開始呢場罷工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">十日時間既文宣 未知係咪足夠 可能係小弟無腦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾個月以來發生既種種事  流過既<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">血</span></span>與淚<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">失去左既前程 手腳 生命 寶貴既自由<br />\n<br />\n破碎左既家庭  所愛之人受到傷害<br />\n<br />\n再加上出盡奶力既文宣  </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">都無辦法換來三日既真罷工</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">下次會再做得更好 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一日唔開槍打死哂我地 <br />\n<br />\n抗爭都會持續落去  <br />\n<br />\n沒有退路與失敗  只有自由與勝利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或許去到呢刻  大家都失去左方向<br />\n<br />\n變得迷惘 不知所措 進退兩難  灰心喪志<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但千奇唔好放棄  懶惰到唔再去行動<br />\n<br />\n堅持落去  勇和一體  絕不退讓<br />\n<br />\n不論一年 兩年 定十年<br />\n<br />\n追求自由民主既火種 永不熄滅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">既然8月5號成功罷到一日<br />\n<br />\n我地就會罷到兩日 三日 更可能係一星期<br />\n<br />\nIt always seems impossible until it's done</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多  <br />\n<br />\n各位手足 堅持落去<br />\n<br />\n煲底見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189ee3691a35cd02721e2eab4c8111d425b8c6c5","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:11:57.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31734299f81b74525b6a752e5e33d4853e7d1068","tid":1683822,"uid":32533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:16:24.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a7c0f63fb7e5a31ba6623a6b3e44eec225d734b6","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:17:28.000Z","msg":"好攰 聽日再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n份工都辭埋  日日罷工 全力抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944534caec8037555f7628c98b12150eb7f61ef8","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:18:33.000Z","msg":"各位要努力說服 叫身邊既人一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722b3510ba0b3c16218a59c0c008e20211d14496","tid":1683822,"uid":57738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d2d004046584f2928ac0eb7c4155c7f54dddf5e","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:22:16.000Z","msg":"當日都需要人出來幫手製造罷工  不被捕為大前提<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0211804cfffff2962d30df57c1446fd0d327deb0","tid":1683822,"uid":178782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:29:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95ebd14f4f9d05e7cc7acd6a75b61d9dc850ad9f","tid":1683822,"uid":179139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:32:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7aa4371bf5408a7df6f39edcaea03082c2b1efdd","tid":1683822,"uid":20298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:37:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7291dfeae1daa99e578c9839b8cf24dd2ec27269","tid":1683822,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c0f63fb7e5a31ba6623a6b3e44eec225d734b6","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:17:28.000Z","msg":"好攰 聽日再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n份工都辭埋  日日罷工 全力抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:38:09.000Z","msg":"日日罷課 全力抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea013a6e37fbbb19e3c33b1e961a01fcb556982","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T21:44:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各位強大既文宣組手足 一齊努力準備呢次既罷工"},{"pid":"4280735e83e35cdbc889b19a4ba331cbde483c31","tid":1683822,"uid":29292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:02:03.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過罷工set deadline好戇鳩？<br />\n「三罷直至光復」會唔會好啲呢？<br />\n比你罷到三日，政府捱到三日又咪繼續迫害市民"},{"pid":"57c46958449d1ea62fce225cee34700d17f4cb5c","tid":1683822,"uid":134033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4280735e83e35cdbc889b19a4ba331cbde483c31","tid":1683822,"uid":29292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:02:03.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過罷工set deadline好戇鳩？<br />\n「三罷直至光復」會唔會好啲呢？<br />\n比你罷到三日，政府捱到三日又咪繼續迫害市民"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:17:04.000Z","msg":"我都想 但奈何呢個行動更難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb5671bda7a0bbc5795217dda6a1e7aa4241316","tid":1683822,"uid":236486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:19:23.000Z","msg":"罷工沒撚用架啦"},{"pid":"e00c1a005315aec6d84794b9d8d19c325c0fc7f9","tid":1683822,"uid":23390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:57:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n罷工先係最有用嘅籌碼"},{"pid":"d6fd376ec66b1cf14c82b30180647b1b825f6931","tid":1683822,"uid":45299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T23:00:04.000Z","msg":"要無限期罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec71042bc2a756e7dd3f086d266f323281bf2aeb","tid":1683822,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4280735e83e35cdbc889b19a4ba331cbde483c31","tid":1683822,"uid":29292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T22:02:03.000Z","msg":"其實有無諗過罷工set deadline好戇鳩？<br />\n「三罷直至光復」會唔會好啲呢？<br />\n比你罷到三日，政府捱到三日又咪繼續迫害市民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T00:00:27.000Z","msg":"無限期罷工真係最有效，有效過我地遊行一百次，又安全又唔洗同埋狗硬碰，可惜講到口臭都無人肯做"},{"pid":"802aee7be997092dfb4b2b182b28e27e7fd89b6b","tid":1683822,"uid":124455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec71042bc2a756e7dd3f086d266f323281bf2aeb","tid":1683822,"uid":172290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4280735e83e35cdbc889b19a4ba331cbde483c31","tid":1683822,"uid":29292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"repl